name: Hot Commodity body chain
description:
Everywhere I go wearing this body chain I get complimented... It's only proper that I start offering it to the masses! Come one come all, join the chain gang, rock it and feel badass with this edgy and out of the ordinary accessory. #Seriously you'll love it, it's a staple for me! 
Made from silver plated, large wide cable chain. Front and back lay in the same fashion.

name: It's Fine tank
description:
No explanation needed. I mean...
THE tank of all tanks. It's absolutely necessary. My motto for everything in life is "it's fine." Even if things don't seem fine, they always turn out to be. Everything is fine all the time, and this, dare I say, is fine.
